text:
Huh? Uh, yeah.
Although it started as a stroll... it ended up being one...
...Are you going for a walk too?

Oh, right! There are fruits in the fridge of the canteen.
Why don't you and the girls have some?

Yeah, true...
But... it's already night, and it's dark outside...

...You're being overly protective.
There are streetlights within the premises.

Yeah... Well... But, you know, I hope you'd really reconsider.
It's an outdoor environment outside isn't it...?

Which means... It's not only humans
that are attracted to the light, you know...

Hmmm... I didn't want to say it directly to you but,
in short... moths──

I'll go get them.
......You said they were in the canteen?
